name: GenuSoft Solutions
overview:
GenuSoft Solutions is a global software development & Services and information technology outsourcing company. Combining proven expertise in technology, and an understanding of emerging business domains, GenuSoft Solutions delivers a range of outsourcing services that includes Custom Application Development, Server Administration, Integration Solutions, product engineering, and IT consulting at affordable prices to small and medium companies globally.

We specialize in custom application development, web development and iOs Apps development. We base on edge technologies and innovative ideas, by which we help our clients to transform their ideas and strategic vision into reality. We realize that your business must keep pace with the speed of thought, and we believe that your ideas and enterprises deserve substantial reinvention. We address these changing needs of your business with solutions that are not only cost-effective but also fast to deploy, highly scalable and reliable. By delivering high quality, cost effective solutions on time to our clients we enable them to focus on their core objectives, and on the gain of competitive advantage.
